Audrey Meadows https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Audrey_Meadows 0 Audrey Meadows (born Audrey Cotter, February 8, 1922 – February 3, 1996) was an American actress best known for her role as the deadpan housewife Alice Kramden on the 1950s American television comedy The Honeymooners.
